instructions: PUT THE PLATE ON THE TABLE CLOTH.
ORDER THE SALAD PLATE ON THE TOP OF THE PLATE.
ORDER THE NAPKIN ON THE TOP OF THE SALAD PLATE.
PUT THE WINE GLASS ON  THE TOP OF THE PLATE.
PUT THE WATER GLASS NEAR BY THE WINE GLASS.
PUT THE SALAD FORK ON LEFT BOTTOM OF THE TABLE CLOTH.
PUT THE DINNER FORK NEAR BY THE SALAD FORK.
PUT THE DINNER KNIFE NEAR BY THE RIGHT OF THE TABLE CLOTH
PUT THE SOUP SPOON NEAR BY THE DINNER KNIFE.
